  ‚áî (is-equiv (Coslice-map-precompose (point x) weird-horn-inclusion‚àô))
coslice-is-left‚áîleft-inner-coslice x
  = (orthogonal‚áîpb-power-is-equiv ‚áî‚Åª¬π)
  ‚àô‚áî top‚áîbot-is-equiv‚ÜêArrow-equiv amap amap-eq module Cov-hom where
